# Product Images Directory

This directory stores product images for the e-commerce store.

## Image Requirements
- Format: JPG or PNG
- Recommended size: 800x800 pixels (square)
- Filename: Use product SKU (e.g., LAP-DELL-001.jpg)

## Upload Images
Upload product images via the admin panel at:
Admin > Products > Edit Product > Upload Image

Or manually upload files here and then add them via the database.
